A River Runs Through It is based on the true story of two fly fishing brothers, Norman and Paul, (Brad Pitt and Craig Sheffer) whose Reverend D. father (Robert Redman), a pastor at a small Church in Montana, heartlessly dumps his wife.
This is one messed up twisted family if I ever saw one! I don't think any of these people took loving each other very seriously whatsoever!
It's another love story between both brothers and women;
